    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center">The eDMS has two different modules of operation</h1><br>
        <div class="col-md-12"><div class="div-image image-container" style="background-image: url('../../../../Themes/SynergySolutions/img/edms-two-module.jpg')"></div><img class="img-fluid no-display" src="assets/img/images/edms-two-module.jpg"></div>
