        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Using the built-in retention engine, remove old documents from the DMS, reducing storage and reducing document search time</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Reduce redundant document storage across the organisation to save space and money.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify"></p>Improves client response for the extended company by coordinating content scattered across multiple platforms and information silos.</div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify"></p>Reduce redundant document storage across the organisation to save space and money.</div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify"></p>With a collaborative framework, you can identify and capitalise on opportunities.</div>
